1. *Æe* se vratim za nekoliko sati. (I will be back in a few hours.)
2. Slažem se sa tim *æe* ti kažem. (I agree with that, I will tell you.)
3. *Æe* se svi sastanemo u parku? (Will we all meet in the park?)
4. *Æe* li sutra biti sunčano? (Will it be sunny tomorrow?)
5. *Æe* li oni prisustvovati vašoj proslavi? (Will they attend your celebration?)
6. *Æe* li ona uspeti da stigne na vreme? (Will she manage to arrive on time?)
7. *Æe* li oni ponoviti isti postupak? (Will they repeat the same procedure?)
8. *Æe* li ovo biti dovoljno? (Will this be enough?)